<template>
   <v-card elevation="3" class="myCardNote">
        <v-card-title>{{title}}</v-card-title>
        <v-card-subtitle>{{date}}</v-card-subtitle>
        <v-card-text class="myCardText">
           {{description}}
        </v-card-text>
        <v-card-actions>
            <v-btn text color="primary">Download</v-btn>
            <v-btn text>Cancel</v-btn>
        </v-card-actions>
    </v-card>
</template>
  
  <script>
  export default {
    name: "CardNote",
    props:{
        title: String,
        description: String,
        date: String
    },
    data: () => ({
      
    }),
    methods: {
      openNewNote() {
        alert("ok");
      },
    },
  };
  </script>
  
  <style>
    .myCardNote{
        background: #adafe7 !important;
        max-height: 180px;
    }
  </style>
